<view class="page"><view class="card"><view class="title">提交本次作业</view><textarea class="field" placeholder="补充文字说明" bindinput="input"/><button class="secondary" bindtap="choose">选择照片或短视频</button><button class="secondary" bindtap="chooseDocument">从微信选择 PDF / Word</button><button class="secondary" bindtap="toggleRecord">{{recording?'停止录音':'录制语音说明'}}</button><view class="muted">已选择 {{files.length}} 个文件；系统会保留首次和每次订正版。</view></view><button class="primary" loading="{{busy}}" disabled="{{busy}}" bindtap="submit">确认提交</button></view>
